has_content.text: Vibrant and lively yet peaceful, our campus is a great place to enrich your mind and body. It’s a place of many facets: exciting and busy, but welcoming and serene.
This is a pretty short caption and might be less than 2 lines.

blockquote.text: "Getting involved and helping the community is really important because it develops that sense of civic identity, so that makes you a lot closer to your community… when you really know what's going on."
